HEADWORD: Air jacket
<hw>Air" jack`et</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A jacket having air-tight
cells, or cavities which can be filled with air, to render persons
buoyant in swimming.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Airless</ent>⟦br⟧
